{"tid":840791,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"波台一向我大曬 我玩曬","createTime":"2018-09-29T05:36:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T05:50:37.000Z","uid":34934,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64c4b1a4329c59ed9c52f02b169d1967d77b88ea","tid":840791,"uid":34934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:36:37.000Z","msg":"足狗掌管一帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解入波台？<br />\n巴閉囉，英雄主義，疊馬。<br />\n我唔妥你，我可以撚你；<br />\n我唔鍾意你，我可以bin你。<br />\n利狗你睥咩呀？出嚟隻揪吖！<br />\n隻揪呀！<br />\n揪我吖！揪吖！<br />\n我揪你你揪我，點呀？<br />\n你見過豬蛇未呀？你見過老鼠未呀？<br />\n你話賓特拿你偶像吖嘛，你見過賓特拿未呀？<br />\n波台揸fit人吖嘛，好巴閉呀？"},{"pid":"df5c8b5014f745d0916aad5ddcbb1b681b1525bf","tid":840791,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"橙！"}]}